{"tid":277953,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紀念國足1-0南韓，“中國足球福地”石碑在長沙揭幕","createTime":"2017-06-10T05:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T05:31:53.000Z","uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c77e665c5ec55fd64e3e3a4415cab017da30ec8","tid":277953,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"北京時間6月9日，&ldquo;中國足球福地&rdquo;石碑在湖南長沙賀龍體育場揭幕。該石碑長9.9米，高3.23米，代表着2017年3月23日中國國家隊在此1-0戰勝南韓國家隊這一難忘的日子；0.56米的厚度代表着56個民族，代表着中華民族團結、友愛、拼搏的精神。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e2ad827468d169cabc129bf081c88b174a2380","tid":277953,"uid":67956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8494b73a0851fab8dd21b59f5abaef762e6bd2d","tid":277953,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:29:05.000Z","msg":"贏多幾次咪成個墳場咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b366f80afb1808b6e8bd9726bca2170febffad","tid":277953,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:29:11.000Z","msg":"真係硬膠到不得了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n赢一場，就要整一個<br />\n咁對家咪好唔得閒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754d830b0a63bac3937ea1eccf96d11a49be6207","tid":277953,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36fe45afd0df529b74fdccf7ffa4ccd371b3d124","tid":277953,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:31:53.000Z","msg